**Project Brief Statement**

The objective of this project is to develop a web application tailored for students that transforms any written content into engaging video formats to enhance learning. By leveraging AI-driven text-to-video conversion, this platform will provide an interactive and accessible way for students to absorb information more effectively. The application will support various content types, ensuring adaptability to different learning needs and preferences. The ultimate goal is to improve comprehension and retention by integrating multimedia elements into the study process.

**Key Features (Prioritized using MoSCoW Framework)**

**Must-Have:**

- AI-driven text-to-video conversion
- Support for multiple content types (PDFs, Word documents, plain text, etc.)
- Voice-over narration with multiple language options
- Subtitle generation for accessibility
- User-friendly interface with drag-and-drop functionality
- Cloud storage integration for saving and accessing content

**Required Pages for MVP:**

1. **Home Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, Navigation Menu (Home, Features, Login, Sign Up)
   - **Hero Section:** App Overview, Call-to-Action (CTA) Button
   - **Feature Highlights:** Grid/List showcasing key features
   - **Testimonials Section:** User feedback and success stories
   - **Footer:** Links to Privacy Policy, Terms of Use, Contact Info

2. **Sign Up / Login Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, Navigation Menu
   - **Form Section:** Email, Password, Social Login Buttons
   - **Forgot Password Link**
   - **CTA Button:** Sign Up / Log In
   - **Footer:** Links to Privacy Policy, Terms of Use

3. **Dashboard Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown, Logout Button
   - **Sidebar:** Navigation (Upload Content, Library, Settings)
   - **Main Section:** Overview of recent videos, Quick Actions (Upload New, Edit, Preview)
   - **Footer:** App Version, Support Link

4. **Upload & Conversion Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **Upload Section:** Drag-and-Drop or Select File Button
   - **Customization Options:** Voice-over Language, Subtitles, Theme Selection
   - **CTA Button:** Convert to Video
   - **Footer:** Support Link

5. **Video Preview Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **Video Player Section:** Preview Video with Play/Pause Controls
   - **Options Panel:** Edit, Save, Download Buttons
   - **Footer:** Support Link

6. **Library / Saved Videos Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **Search & Filter Section:** Search Bar, Sorting Options
   - **Video List/Grid:** Thumbnails with Titles, Edit & Delete Buttons
   - **Footer:** Support Link

7. **Settings Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **User Preferences:** Language, Notifications, Privacy Settings
   - **Cloud Integration:** Connect to Google Drive/AWS
   - **CTA Button:** Save Changes
   - **Footer:** Support Link

8. **Help / FAQ Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **FAQ Section:** Common Questions and Answers
   - **Contact Support Section:** Email Form or Chatbot
   - **Footer:** Support Link

9. **Profile Page**

   - **Header:** Logo, User Profile Dropdown
   - **User Details Section:** Name, Email, Subscription Status
   - **Edit Profile Button**
   - **Logout Button**
   - **Footer:** Support Link

10. **Error / Not Found Page**

- **Header:** Logo
- **Error Message Section:** 404 Not Found / Unexpected Error
- **CTA Button:** Return to Home
- **Footer:** Support Link

**Technical Requirements**

- Frontend: React.js or Vue.js for a responsive UI
- Backend: Node.js with Express for handling requests
- AI Integration: GPT-based models for text processing and video generation
- Video Processing: FFmpeg or a third-party API like Synthesia
- Database: PostgreSQL or Firebase for user data storage
- Cloud Storage: AWS S3 or Google Cloud Storage for video hosting
- Authentication: OAuth2 or Firebase Authentication for secure login
- Deployment: Docker for containerization and scalability
- API Development: RESTful APIs for smooth integration with external services

